onger on this visit we would have tried it.There is Wi-Fi in the lobby, although we were able to also access our email up on the top floor through other connections. There is also a computer in the lobby, which is very cozy.The hotel has a terrific parking arrangement (by San Francisco standards) with the garage across the street.This hotel is a gem. Very French. In fact, there were several French and German Nationals staying there. When we checked in, we were warmly welcomed by an aged, Golden Retriever, who even rode up in the elevator with us. We will go back to this lovely place.	
